title: BONUS Ep. #6 | Eric Says STAY HOME
description:
Reminder to STAY HOME! Eric is back with a bonus episode and he has a lot to say about quarantine news, his mom, and his feelings. How do you feel? It’s okay to be anxious and stressed because you are NOT alone. Stay safe, everyone, and remember to breathe!
Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.
Episodes are presented by @thedivestudios
Connect with us on all social media platforms @daebakshow and at http://www.divestudios.io/daebakshow !
